	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=13&mid=100515087259930>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=13&mid=100515087259930>New characters</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=13&mid=100515087259930#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Wed, Nov 7th 11:34 AM 2001</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=116763><span id= >boxorox</span></a><br><span id=notbold>14 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Ok, here is my 2cp on how to build and work a chanter. Most of you may disagree but I have found this is the way it works for everything. <br><br>1. Choose no god! If you do you will regret later. Chanters are supposed to be able to go anywhere. If you choose a god you will be out working on your faction instead of working on your skills in that area you should be hated in. <br><br>2. Dump everything you can into int at lower levels then start trading to Cha when you get to like 200 int or close. Cha is only for selling, mez for really really high levels, and charm spells. If you are charming a lot of stuff you are in a bad group or soloing. If soloing go back to group thats what you do. Soloing can be done, but why solo 1 thing that takes all your mana when you can group and take out 4 times the amount with no mana lost really. Only high level mez is not time based. Check it and see.<br><br>3 Skillz : To make skills go up you need int. To make items you need Wisdom. Remember this or you will find out you wished you saved some wis items as you are making that snow griff egg souffle for the prayer shawl in Thurg and fail it! <br><br>4. Dont worry about money so much. You will find that even if you dont loot you will be taken care of by good groups. If they arent splitting cash move on to one that will. You need to med more than loot, and believe me your group will split when they see you mez half the population of norrath and live to make it through it. <br><br>5. Always Always Always keep tash up. That blue con might have an MR or 999 and you not know it. Dont think so. Check out next time Frankle the Pirate (level 30)&nbsp;&nbsp;gets beat on by a level 55 and the level 55 goes down screaming the lil pirate killed em. Tash will save you more times than not. And yes it aggros mega, but you need to let the mellee peeps beat on em a little then you tash and slow. You will see what I mean. And the melee peeps will love you every time. <br><br>6. Never Never Never charge for Mind candy. I have seen chanters go for hours shouting for a port or rez (seen em offer 500 pp), and I shout it one time and get it almost every time ( for free) . I never charge for mind candy, and people remember that I helped them more than they helped me. You would be amazed at the times I have seen that same person ask me how I do it and then turn around and charge 10 pp for mind buffs only to scream for port 2 mins later. <br><br>This is getting long so ill only add this. When in groups Clarity in the following order, and spread it so it works out for time. <br><br>First time Clarity schedule.<br>You have time to med for this one.<br>Yourself, first melee (even if they dont need its a timer for them), all casters, then healers lowest to highest.<br><br>Clarity on the fight. <br><br>Yourself, Highest level healers to lowest, all other casters, then hybrids if needed. <br><br>You will find that when yours starts to pop on the first time you cast on yourself to save time and that melee person that complained earlier will start saying clarity dropping. Guess what you now have two mins to get that healer a clarity, and the whole group knows it. And they wont be complaining about you getting to the healers first if they are smart. <br><br>Sorry for the long post but I hope this will help the little guys that are starting up in the game. Feel free to comment on what I said. Not everyone agrees with me on a lot. But if you dig and look you will see what I say is true. <br><br>Boxorox - Cazic Thule Server<br></p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
