	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I am a lvl 34 High Elf Enchanter and have been playing in Overthere since lvl 30.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have found a great way to make alot of exp real fast.  All that is needed is you,  a person to SOW the group, a healer, and someone to pull/tank, any other class is there just to speed things along.<br>First.  Move along side the mountain to an area near the ledge leading to FM zone.  Have everyone with full mana, and sow.  Best for you to get any hp buffs you can,  and speed buff everyone with Augmen.  Yes everyone for it helps you dodge being hit and stunned.  Then Send out your puller to grab a mob of 6 to 7 monsters.  Yes I said 6 to 7.  Have the puller run in a big circle in front of the group while you single target mez each one.  When all but one is mezzed tell your group to attack that one while you keep the others mezzed.  When that one dies,  you tell the group which monster to kill next and so on.  The most important things to tell your group is not to attack until you say attack, otherwise they will keep breaking your mez and everything will go down hill quickly.  also make sure the tank runs in a large circle in front of the group,  and that he is not running to close to the group otherwise the mob may agro on your group.  I made from lvl 32 to 33 1/2 in less than 3 hrs using this technique.  By the end the time all the monsters are dead,  Your group should have at least half there mana left.<br>From your friendly Quicky Mart Drug Store Owner)<br>Fiev Sixx<br>Immortal Dragonsbane (Mith Marr Server)</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
