	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Fri, Nov 2nd 6:57 PM 2001</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I completely agree with your assessment of the charisma impact determined by the level of the mob.&nbsp;&nbsp;Many people will argue with you until they're blue in the face, but just try mezzing black, yellow and red cons with no charisma gear/buffs (near a zone, I suggest) and then again with 75 points of charisma gear.  Huge difference.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
